"hinweg zu speichern, aktivieren Sie die [[Thunderbird-E-Mail-Client|persistent_storage/configure#thunderbird]]-Funktion \n"
"des persistenten Speichers.</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "</div>\n"
msgstr "</div>\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"For more documentation, visit the official [*Thunderbird* Support](https://"
"support.mozilla.org/en-US/products/thunderbird) website."
msgstr ""
"Für weitere Dokumentation besuchen Sie die offizielle Website des "
"[*Thunderbird*-Supports](https://support.mozilla.org/de/products/"
"thunderbird)."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<div class=\"bug\">\n"
msgstr "<div class=\"bug\">\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
